@houseroad I have upgraded both pytorch python API and libtorch to version 1.0.0.dev20181121 and now my code works fine. Thank you!

However, I am getting inference time much slower than the python model, is this normal?
For Resnet50 for example, the python model gets makes 200 ms per frame but the serialized model gets 600 ms per frame after the de-serialization in C++.
